node.text: I have been to Lake MacDonald 50 times, but it is still one of the most beautiful places I can imagine.
I took this lil video earlier this year. I totally forgot about it, counting down til winter! Who else hangs out in the backcountry?
One of my favorite trips this year was to the Tantalus Mountains in BC.  Fun times, snowboarding, and couscous, what more could you ask for?  New video up on the Youtubes. Link is up!
I love the outdoors! What's my favorite short hike in the Seattle area? Click the link in my bio to find out in my new YouTube video. Thanks Y'all!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Morgan Phillips on December 16, 2021 tagging @morganphillips, and @backcountry. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Getting outside is almost always what I need to unwind and slow down—whether I’m climbing, mountain biking, split boarding or backpacking. Having the right gear truly makes all the difference. 

I’ve put together a Gift Guide with some of my favorite gear from @backcountry and they’re also having a sale for the holidays! You can find my Gift Guide in my stories or by clicking the ‘Guide’ tab on my profile. #findyourbackcountry

node.text:
GIVING TUESDAY WEEKLONG EVENT:  I am so proud to team up with The Walkabout Foundation to help people in need! @walkaboutorg is dedicated to restoring dignity, freedom and independence to people with mobility disabilities, by providing wheelchairs and rehabilitation in the developing world and by funding research to find a cure for paralysis.

On November 30th, #GivingTuesday, a day of global giving, we have decided to give back to @walkaboutorg by taking part in their virtual #WalkaboutHolidayAuction. Instead of donating a monetary value this year, give back by bidding on one of the items in their auction and join in on the guilt-free holiday shopping knowing that 100% of the proceeds go to their global projects. 

There are just some examples of the prints you can choose! 

Visit www.givergy.uk/walkaboutholidayauction to start bidding!

#givingtuesday #charity #donate #notsponsored
